{
  "chapter": 38,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙潜入信陵君府后宅小楼，在枝春与少原君幽会的房间中躲过巡逻，得到刘巢等家将协助，通过秘道进入藏宝库找到《鲁公秘录》并临摹替换。信陵君假意安排雅夫人等人返回赵国，实则扣留赵倩为人质。纪嫣然主动来访项少龙，以比武为名试探其剑法实力，被项少龙以飞虹剑脱手加飞脚奇招制服。纪嫣然表明心意，项少龙因身负重任不敢接受，含恨告别。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少原君",
      "listener": "char_zhi_chun",
      "text": "枝春你定是没有把窗子关好，看！窗被风吹开来哩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "枝春",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "没有理由的，让我去把它关上，天气真冷！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "枝春",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吹熄了蜡烛哩！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "枝春",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有人在吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "武士",
      "listener": "char_zhi_chun",
      "text": "夫人有什么吩咐？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "枝春",
      "listener": "char_liu_chao",
      "text": "刘巢！什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_chao",
      "speaker_name": "刘巢",
      "listener": "char_zhi_chun",
      "text": "没什么！刚见到有只耗子走过，吓了一跳。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "枝春",
      "listener": "char_liu_chao",
      "text": "少君肚子饿，小盈她们又睡着了，麻烦你们到膳房使人弄些酒菜来。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_chao",
      "speaker_name": "刘巢",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们正在谈起兵卫，兵卫到这里有什么事，我们怎样才可帮上忙？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_chao",
      "speaker_name": "刘巢",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "兵卫请稍等一下！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_chao",
      "speaker_name": "刘巢",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "兵卫放心下去，我们给你把风。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_liu_chao",
      "text": "最好你和我一起下去，必要时可由你把那东西放回原处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_liu_chao",
      "text": "切不要把这事告诉其他三个人，到我们有方法离开大梁时，才顺手偷走几件作盘缠，记着万勿妄起贪念，否则人为财死，鸟为食亡，到时连命也要丢掉。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_chao",
      "speaker_name": "刘巢",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "兵卫教训得好！刘巢知道了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "为了你的事，昨夜我一夜没睡苦思，终于想出了妥善的安排。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我有事要和兵卫商量，所有人都不得踏进这里来！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "昨晚有没有打动嫣然的芳心？听说龙阳君和嚣魏牟都应邀去了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "text": "不要说哩！那种聚会哪有我插言的余地！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "并不是这样，你的想法很有创造性，谭邦便很欣赏你呢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙吃过早点吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我真糊涂，刚把人赶走，你坐一会儿，让我吩咐下人把早点弄来。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "早点立即奉上，来！让我告诉你我的计划。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我会使人假造文书，今天送到大王处，让赵雅和贵属全体返回赵国，只留下你和赵倩两人。赵雅是我邀来的客人，龙阳君亦无权反对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "text": "那真好极了，不过可否让他们早点走呢？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "假若这么小的事亦做不到，会教少龙小看我了，好吧！我会安排雅夫人等今午出城，与贵属会合后立即起程，少龙放心好了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "text": "那赵倩的问题又如何解决？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我会派人假扮她让你送入宫去，再找隐秘地方把她藏起来，我信陵君向天立誓，无论事情成功与否，我也会把她不损毫发地送回赵国去。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙满意我的安排吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "text": "非常满意，到时我一定不会有负所托！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙你去见她吧！说不定她看上你呢！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "纪小姐！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "可以腾点空闲时间吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "若只是一会儿，便没有问题。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那随嫣然来吧！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "绝对的权力，使人绝对的腐化，嫣然还是首次听到这么一针见血和富有智慧的话，先生真有勇气。昨夜你走后，所有人包括嫣然在内，都失去了说话的兴趣。嫣然一夜没睡，反复思量先生说过的每一个字，并想着先生说这话时那深信不疑的神采。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项先生为何会和信陵君来见嫣然呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "纪小姐总是会如此逐个询问慕名来访的客人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项先生是第一个令嫣然想问这问题的人，坦白告诉嫣然，她是否令你生厌？所以每次都急着要走，现在又想着怎样离开这辆马车呢？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我从未见过像你那么测不透的人，说话都藏在心底里，逼得没有法子才露上半手。嫣然多么希望和你秉烛夜谈，畅所欲言呢！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "若还觉得嫣然并不讨厌，便下车吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你躲到远处去，半个时辰后才可回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙！我是奉大王之命来把你杀死的，应战吧！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "小姐说笑吧！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "谁和你说笑？看剑！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "终于肯露出真功夫哩！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "不服气吗？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "嫣然怎会不服气呢？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "那你怎样向你的大王交差？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么交差？嫣然不明白项先生你在说什么。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "原来你在骗我。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "还不拖人家起来吗？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要怪嫣然好吗？若非如此，怎能试出你的盖世……嘻……盖世脚法，人家那处仍很疼呢！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙你发怒的神态真好看！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "想不到才艺双全的纪才女也会骗人，还扮得这么像。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你不奇怪为何人家想试你的剑法吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "你想看看项某人是否有资格做你的未来夫婿，是吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "只说对一半，因为尚未到那种地步，而你亦只是勉强及格罢了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "直到今天，你还是第一个入围者，若你真想追求人家，嫣然可以尽量予你方便和机会。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "爱情是男女间一种微妙的感觉，发乎自然，哪有像你这般诸多考较的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "说得非常动听，比任何人都要好，所以嫣然知道你只是因某种原因扮作不喜欢人家，但你看人家的眼神却透露出你内心的秘密。尤其刚才你把人家压在草地上时，嫣然更清楚你对我的心意。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "究竟要回信陵君府，还是回嫣然的雅湖小筑？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快转左！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "请在前面街口停下，我要下车。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项先生，纪嫣然真是令你那么毫不留恋吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "小姐是项某人一生所遇到的女子中最动人的尤物，但时机上太不适当了，很快小姐会明白我的苦衷，忘了我吧！好吗？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "嫣然明白了，若有什么困难，记着纪嫣然会不顾一切来帮助你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 452
    }
  ],
